steps.desc: Loosely assemble the driven gear set and push fit into the elbow joint
Slide the aluminium tube over the threaded rod and push fit the lower bearing
Slip the belt round the pulley - this be connected later
Push the servo brackets onto the servo, optionally screw them into place
Bolt through the aluminium channels and servo brackets
Bolt through the aluminium channels and elbow joint
Screw the wrist bracket onto the wrist servo
Push the spoon assembly into the wrist bracket
Screw through the bracket into the servo fixings
Push M2 nuts into the back of the servo fixing tabs
Attach the spoon holder to the servo
